<!-- 
  To ensure the best readability for users, the lines are split into two columns: base and VAT. 
  For example, in the UI, code 01 is displayed with its description and its value in the "base"
column. 
  The corresponding VAT, code 02, its value is shown in the "VAT" column.

  As a result in the code: when summing up tax due in code 17, for the value of code 02, I refer to
line 1 (sk_01) and its VAT label, 
